'''Tacto''' was one of the [[Twin Cities (Radnor)|Twin Cities]] of the planet [[Radnor/Legends|Radnor]], the other being [[Aubendo]].

When Radnor faced a bioplague in the years leading up to the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], Tacto was in one of the few areas unaffected by it. Tacto was in the [[Clear Sector]], divided from its sister city's [[Isolation Sector]] by an [[energy gate]].

